snippet: Casey birdied the 18th hole for a six-under-par 66 and a share of the first-round lead with Jimmy Walker and Zach Johnson in the Hero World Challenge in Nassau.
abstract: Paul Casey, Jimmy Walker and Zach Johnson share first round lead at Hero World Challenge golf tournament; other golf news noted.
